{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Automation"}], "prev": {"link": "../update_consent_block/", "title": "Update Consent Block"}, "next": {"link": "../update_topics_block/", "title": "Update Topics Block"}, "title": "Update Lists", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"update-lists\">\n<h1>Update Lists<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#update-lists\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">The <strong>Update Lists</strong> block allows you add or remove contacts from a list.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">To use this block, you will need to have navigated to a workflow design tab. Click <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/design_a_workflow.html\">here</a> to do so from <strong>Automation</strong>. Refer to <strong>Campaign</strong> and <strong>Phone</strong> guides for other workflows.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Place an <strong>Update Lists</strong> block in your workflow where desired</p></li>\n<li><p>Select <strong>Add to list</strong> or <strong>Remove from list</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Choose a list</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Select an existing list</p></li>\n<li><p>Alternatively, click <strong>Add New</strong> to create a new <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/crm/guides/programs/lists.html\">list</a> (this list will automatically be chosen)</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Done</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>In the workflow, you can now click <strong>show more</strong> to display the list that will be updated and if a contact will be added/removed</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/automation/guides/workflows/update_topics_block", "Update Topics Block", "N", "next"], ["users/automation/guides/workflows/update_consent_block", "Update Consent Block", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/automation/guides/workflows/update_lists_block.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Update Lists</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/automation/guides/workflows/update_lists_block", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}